Lecturer<br />Email: brittanygrubbs@advising.ufl.edu</h3>
<p>In my role as a lecturer, I teach classes in the Beyond120 program and coordinate the Alumni Internship Program. I am originally from the Jacksonville area, but moved to Orlando to attend UCF and earn a Bachelor’s degree. I also have a Master’s degree in Mass Communications from UF, and I’m currently a doctoral student in the Higher Education Administration program here at UF as well. In my spare time, I enjoy volunteering, spending time with friends and family, being involved in church, and of course, going to Gator games!</p>
